# Concept Distill Rule

Use this rule when the user wants to turn a repo-specific lesson into a reusable concept note for the Obsidian vault.

## Task

Transform implementation-specific learning into a durable concept note for the Obsidian vault.

## Instructions

- Remove project noise unless it is essential.
- Extract the principle, symptoms, failure modes, and practical heuristics.
- Prefer reusable language over timeline language.
- Keep examples short.

## Output schema

````md
---
id: CONCEPT-slug
title: "..."
date: YYYY-MM-DD
source_tool: cursor
source_project: repo-name
tags: [concept, engineering]
status: evergreen
---

